'''Ghost''' is one of six [[direwolf]] cubs that are found by the children of [[House Stark]]. Ghost is adopted and raised by [[Jon Snow]]. Ghost is an albino, with white fur and red eyes. He was the runt of the litter when he was born, though he quickly grew to be as big as the rest of his siblings.

